Macaulay2Editor
Advanced text editor for Macaulay2.

Written in C++ using Qt and KDE libraries.
The text editor component used is KTextEditor from the KDE sdk.

Features:
Autocompletion.
Documentation viewer.
Syntax highlighting.
Integrated terminal for Macaulay2.
File browser.

run dependencies:
  libgdbm
  kde4
  sqlite3
  qt
  Macaulay2







